name: Baby Boo
description: At Baby Boo, we are passionate about bringing joy and uniqueness to the world of NFTs. Our collection of adorable ghosts is not just art; It is a manifestation of creativity and community. We believe in creating a space where holders not only own a piece of digital art, they also share the delightful experience of being part of the Baby Boo family. In addition to our collection of unique NFTs, discover the benefits of our token, games, rewards and utilities. Welcome to the Baby Boo family.
